name: MotivateMe
0:
”Alexa motivate me”
”I need motivation”
”Tell me a motivational quote”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: motivate me
des: This skill will help Alexa help you. Find happiness through quotes to help uplift you and motivate you. Whenever you feel like you need a little boost, just say: "Alexa, motivate me". With this skill, you are just a second away from a motivational quote that will give you strength and direction in your life. Try it today!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
